                    "body": "I`m using this solution but how do I do to validate the ajax request after generating a new hash with this solution. Should I create a new emtpy form with the hash and execute $hashform->isValid($jsonObj)\r\n\r\nCan you help me please",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=mongaru",
                        "name": "mongaru",
                        "displayName": "mongaru",
